(483, 2938, '1413348723916_data', '{\"id\":\"1413348723916\",\"shortcode\":\"ppb_text\",\"ppb_text_title\":\"Tagline\",\"ppb_text_layout\":\"fixedwidth\",\"ppb_text_background\":\"\",\"ppb_text_background_parallax\":\"\",\"ppb_text_custom_css\":\"\",\"ppb_text_content\":\"%5Btg_header%20title=%22Welcome%20to%20Asia%20with%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%22%5D%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09Simply%20speaking%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20do%20only%20adventure%E2%80%9D,%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20is%20bespoke%20trailblazer%20premier%20Authentic%20Himalayan%20Outdoors%20,%20and%20provide%20tailor-made%20adventure%20holiday%20across%20Nepal%20&%20Myanmar%20Himalayas.%20We%20are%20the%20team%20of%20dedicated%20adventure%20industry%20professionals%20who%20are%20all%20passionate%20about%20Adventure.%20Our%20passion%20is%20our%20business;%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20guiding%20experience%20in%20adventure%20tourism%20field%20in%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar%20and%20still%20do%20so.%20Our%20first%20priority%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20do%20the%20adventure%E2%80%A6%20you%20experience%20the%20adventure.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20be%20fooled%20by%20others%20offering%20%E2%80%9Cone%20stop%E2%80%9D%20online%20shopping%20only%20to%20be%20shuffled%20among%20the%20true%20providers%20once%20you%20arrive.%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20has%20created%20an%20entire%20life%20around%20taking%20people%20in%20both%20Himalayas.%20First%20we%20listen%20to%20what%20you%20want%20out%20of%20trip%20and,%20give%20us%20your%20time%20frame,%20date%20and%20budget,%20and%20then%20we%20carefully%20and%20perfectly%20design%20an%20individual%20tailor-made%20holiday%20adventure%20to%20match%20your%20time%20frame,%20working%20to%20your%20budget%20and%20with%20an%20absolute%20commitment%20in%20quality%20and%20safety%20to%20suits%20your%20exact%20requirements%20and%20explores%20your%20interests%E2%80%99%20places%20at%20your%20own%20speed.%20Quite%20simply,%20we%20do%20it%20better%20and%20safer%20because%20it%20matters%20more%20to%20us%20and%20it%20is%20our%20driving%20passion%20and%20single%20commitment.%20Our%20holidays%20are%20all%20about%20excitement,%20and%20journey%20through%20the%20natural%20beauty%20and%20cultural%20diversity%20of%20some%20of%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20remotest%20areas.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20guide%20you%20up%20to%20the%20most%20exciting%20wilderness%20Himalaya%20and%20introduce%20you%20to%20our%20favorite%20destinations%20in%20style%20with%20safety.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20set%20recipe%20either%20fix%20date-%20they%E2%80%99re%20tailor-made%20down%20to%20the%20finest%20detail%20around%20Travelers%20tastes%20and%20interests.%20We%20work%20with%20genuine%20locally-owned%20services%20wherever%20possible%20apart%20from%20our%20own%20trips.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EYour%20Adventure-Your%20Way.%20%3C/strong%3EFar%20more%20than%20just%20a%20catchy%20and%20flexible%20in%20our%20Slogan,%20Level%20of%20difficulty%20and%20style%20of%20adventure%20are%20tailored%20to%20your%20ability%20level%20so%20with%20us%20you%E2%80%99re%20the%20principle%20of%20choosing%20your%20own%20adventure%20that%20you%20have%20dreamed%20and%20imagine.%20We%20are%20good%20listener!%20We%20believe%20that%20the%20best%20adventure%20is%20created%20through%20collaboration.%20We%20are%20thrilled%20to%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20offer%20such%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20trips.%20We%20also%20realize%20that%20this%20can%20create%20confusion.%20We%20are%20a%20fantastic%20resource%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20helping%20you%20choose%20the%20trip%20that%20is%20perfect%20for%20you%20and%20your%20group.%20Please%20feel%20free%20to%20call%20or%20email%20with%20any%20questions%20you%20might%20have,%20we%20love%20to%20help.%20Often%20after%20a%20brief%20conversation%20with%20one%20of%20our%20staff%20the%20answers%20become%20clear.%20So%20we%20ensure%20that%20our%20staff%20complements%20your%20ideas,%20instead%20of%20overriding%20them.%20We%20provide%20the%20structure%20to%20your%20journey,%20offered%20new%20type%20of%20travel%20adventure-%20Get%20inspired%20by%20the%20adventure%20ideas%20on%20our%20website.%20Then%20speak%20to%20us%20for%20first-hand%20adventure%20expert%20advice%20and%20if%20you\'re%20ready,%20start%20planning%20your%20trip%20in%20detail.%20%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20work%20hard%20to%20provide%20an%20experience%20that%20is%20more%20than%20any%20multi%20day%E2%80%99s%20adventure%20trip%20or%20a%20day%20spent.%20%3C/strong%3EWe%20will%20design%20a%20trip%20around%20you,%20strive%20to%20offer%20real%20insight%20the%20untouched%20nature,%20people%20and%20their%20culture,%20and%20away%20from%20crowds,%20even%20commercial%20route%20we%20do%20different%20and%20unique%20way,%20and%20show%20you%20the%20real%20highlights%20in%20a%20different%20light,%20and%20introduce%20you%20to%20places%20and%20experience%20that%20others%20never%20been%20and%20many%20might%20are%20missing,%20We%20strive%20to%20ensure%20that%20time%20spent%20with%20us%20is%20time%20that%20you%20will%20always%20look%20back%20on%20fondly.%20We%20want%20to%20leave%20you%20with%20memories%20that%20bring%20a%20smile%20to%20your%20face%20no%20matter%20where%20you%20are,%20no%20matter%20what%20you%20are%20doing,%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20time%20has%20passed%20and%20no%20matter%20how%20far%20you%20are%20from%20your%20Home%20sweet%20Home.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20pride%20ourselves%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20our%20trips%20and%20our%20ability%20to%20work%20with%20our%20guests.%20%3C/strong%3ESince%20the%20spring%20of%202013%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20has%20been%20offering%20the%20finest%20authentic%20outdoor%20adventures%20available,%20period.%20In%20an%20industry%20that%20is%20often%20about%20tight%20schedules%20and%20ordering%20your%20adventure%20by%20the%20numbers%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20is%20more%20than%20happy%20to%20customize%20any%20of%20our%20trips%20in%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar.%20%20%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20the%20guest%20to%20provide%20exactly%20what%20they%20envision.%3C/strong%3E%20We%E2%80%99ve%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20organized%20family%20friendly%20adventure%20that%20suits%20for%20your%20little%20one%20and%20the%20elderly%20parents,%20newlyweds%20honeymoon%20and%20anniversary%20trip%20in%20Himalaya,%20Himalaya%20yoga%20and%20meditation%20trek,%20corporate%20team%20building%20events,%20Himalayan%20Community%20Trek%20which%20we%20provides%20health,%20education,%20sports%20with%20multi%20play%20grounds,%20educating%20people%20and%20children%20about%20Rubbish%20management%20knowledge%20from%20their%20very%20little%20age%20and%20encourage%20them%20in%20environmental%20campaign.%20We%20have%20designed%20and%20run%20specialized%20training%20courses%20to%20become%20a%20mountain,%20trekking,%20rafting%20and%20just%20multi%20adventure%20guide,%20National%20and%20International%20Army%20training,%20expeditions%20and%20youth%20leadership%20programs%20that%20offer%20students%20adventures%20and%20learning%20experience%20in%20a%20world%20they%20couldn\'t%20imagine%20existed.%20We%20have%20helped%20major%20international%20and%20national%20universities%20with%20trips%20focused%20on%20adventure,%20geology,%20photography%20and%20creative%20writing.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20hosted,%20organized%20and%20supported%20the%20national%20and%20international%20adventure%20movie%20makers%20and%20journalists%20and%20World%20Charity%20Trip%20for%20disable%20children%20to%20orphanage%20house%20and%20association%20from%20around%20the%20world.%20We%20did%20these%20trips%20not%20because%20we%20offered%20them,%20we%20did%20these%20trips%20because%20we%20love%20to%20and%20you%20asked.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20are%20owned%20and%20operated%20by%20our%20guides%20with%20staffed%20and%20people%20who%20make%20their%20living%20in%20the%20Himalaya%20outdoors.%3C/strong%3E%20Again,%20No%20matter%20the%20season%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20the%20owners,%20guides%20and%20staff%20in%20outdoors%20in%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar%20Himalaya.%20The%20reason%20we%20run%20adventure%20is%20because%20we%20love%20nature.%20So%20we%20climb%20mountains,%20trek%20to%20the%20base%20camps,%20whitewater%20rafting%20and%20kayaking,%20rock%20climbing,%20canyoning,%20caving,%20mountain%20bike,%20mountain%20flight,%20paragliding,%20bungee%20jumping,%20wildlife%20safari,%20%E2%80%9CMyanmar%20Source%20to%20the%20Sea%20or%20Sea%20to%20the%20Source%20Adventure%20Journey%E2%80%9D%20and%20share%20adventure%20experiences%20with%20both%20old%20and%20new%20friends%20(that%E2%80%99s%20you!).%20Our%20trips%20are%20designed%20and%20run%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20providing%20the%20highest%20quality%20experience%20and%20spreading%20our%20passion%20for%20our%20mountains%20and%20rivers,%20not%20to%20maximize%20our%20profit%20margins.%20We%20like%20to%20make%20this%20evident%20from%20the%20moment%20our%20guests%20walk%20in%20our%20door%20and%20experience%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20authentic%20adventure%20journey%20through%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar,%20until%20they%20hug%20us%20and%20goodbye%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%20and%20until%20we%20meet%20again!%20The%20kind%20of%20authenticity%20and%20hospitality%20you\'ll%20find%20here%20can\'t%20be%20faked%20because%20we%20work%20from%20our%20heart.%20Come%20and%20see%20for%20yourself,%20or%20meet%20our%20team%20here.%20In%20short,%20we%20love%20the%20outdoors%20adventure.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20have%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20experience%20and%20expertise.%3C/strong%3E%20Put%20simply%20and%20telling%20the%20truth,%20our%20trips%20come%20after%20decades%20of%20working%20and%20exploring%20experience%20in%20adventure%20field%20in%20both%20countries%20as%20an%20adventure%20guide.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20there%20done%20that%20and%20become%20better%20for%20it.%20%20our%20love%20and%20experience%20of%20wild%20places%20and%20our%20constant%20desire%20to%20be%20outside,%20we%20have%20gained%20a%20knowledge%20base%20that%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20won%20through%20school%20or%20training%20alone.%20Mother%20Nature%20is%20our%20first%20teacher%20and%20Himalayas%20is%20our%20classroom%20and%20playground%20(which%20makes%20us%20among%20the%20luckiest%20people%20in%20the%20world).%20%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3E%0A%09%09We%20have%20extensive%20knowledge%20of%20and%20certification%20in%20mountain%20climbing%20safety,%20techniques%20and%20dealing%20with%20high%20altitude%20sickness,%20wilderness%20first%20aid%20and%20CPR,%20whitewater%20rescue,%20safety%20and%20technique.%3C/strong%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20a%20deep%20reservoir%20of%20personal%20experience,%20each%20of%20our%20adventure%20guides%20is%20licensed%20by%20the%20Nepal%20&%20Myanmar%20Mountaineering%20Association,%20Trekking%20Agencies%20Association%20of%20Nepal,%20Nepal%20Association%20of%20Rafting%20Agencies,%20Nepal%20Kayak%20&%20Canoe%20Club%20and%20International%20Rafting%20Federation%20certified%20Grade%204/5%20raft%20guides,%20trip%20leaders%20and%20kayakers,%20swift%20water%20certified%20and%20insured.%20Our%20climbing%20guides%20are%20NRCS%20certified%20for%20the%20terrain%20they%20operate%20in.%20Our%20guides%20are%20intimately%20acquainted%20with%20not%20only%20the%20mountain,%20river%20and%20rock,%20but%20also%20the%20incredible%20surroundings%20of%20the%20Himalaya%20wilderness%20places%20and%20with%20local%20communities%20in%20both%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EWe%20take%20your%20adventure%20seriously.%20%3C/strong%3EFar%20more%20than%20just%20a%20catchy%20slogan,%20in%20reality%20adventure%20is%20all%20about%20%3Cstrong%3ERisk%20&%20Fun%3C/strong%3E,%20So%20there%20for%20it%20is%20our%20core%20philosophy%20and%20acknowledges%20our%20role%20as%20professionals%20in%20providing%20fun%20and%20safe%20adventures%20(which%20makes%20us%20among%20the%20luckiest%20people%20in%20the%20world,%20we%20are%20well%20aware!)%20in%20an%20environment%20that%20demands%20serious%20skill,%20experience,%20and%20judgment.%20The%20mountain%20we%20climb,%20trails%20we%20trek%20and%20rivers%20in%20which%20we%20paddle%20are%20wild,%20remote,%20untouched,%20and%20subject%20to%20the%20unpredictability%20of%20nature,%20and%20weather%20meaning%20that%20safety%20is%20far%20from%20automatic%20and%20risks%20need%20to%20be%20properly%20managed.%20It%20goes%20without%20saying%20that%20safety%20is%20always%20our%20first%20and%20unforgotten%20priority%20in%20all%20of%20our%20activities.%20This%20commitment%20runs%20through%20every%20part%20of%20our%20outdoors%20adventure%20operation,%20from%20the%20equipment%20we%20provide,%20to%20the%20professionalism%20of%20our%20guides,%20to%20the%20way%20we%20run%20our%20trips%20and%20selecting%20our%20local%20and%20international%20partners.%20This%20is%20the%20key%20ingredient%20in%20our%20Himalayan%20homegrown%20recipe%20for%20serious%20fun!%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EOur%20love,%20respect%20and%20role%20for%20nature%20and%20peoples%20throughout%20adventure,%20%3C/strong%3EAs%20an%20Adventure%20person,%20relationship%20with%20the%20nature%20is%20one%20that%20few%20others%20can%20truly%20understand.%20The%20Himalayas,%20for%20all%20its%20massive%20mountains%20peaks%20and%20impressive%20geography,%20is%20actually%20an%20incredibly%20fragile%20environment.%20Deforestation,%20erosion%20and%20overpopulation%20in%20the%20mountains%20regions%20are%20becoming%20major%20problems%20in%20some%20areas.%20Adventure%20tourism,%20which%20has%20given%20new%20opportunities%20and%20resources,%20has%20also%20had%20a%20large%20effect%20on%20the%20consumption%20of%20natural%20resources.%20Our%20lives%20have%20revolved%20around%20rivers,%20mountain%20and%20people.%20These%20areas%20have%20captivated%20our%20imagination%20and%20our%20hearts,%20and%20throughout%20all%20the%20years%20inspired%20us.%20For%20over%20two%20decades%20of%20adventure%20running%20experience%20we%20have%20gaining%20knowledge%20and%20appreciation%20for%20those%20little%20known%20areas.%20In%20our%20daily%20lives,%20Mother%20Nature%20reigns%20supreme%E2%80%94%20she%20seduces%20us%20with%20her%20beauty,%20awes%20us%20with%20her%20might,%20and%20charms%20us%20with%20her%20style.%20What%20she%20often%20fails%20to%20show%20us%20is%20how%20vulnerable%20she%20really%20is%20and%20how%20much%20our%20actions%20hurt%20her.%20She%20depends%20on%20those%20who%20know%20her%20best%20to%20help%20others%20understand%20and%20respect%20her%20needs.%20Here%20we%20recognize%20our%20duty%20to%20educate%20and%20inspire%20every%20one%20of%20our%20guests%20through%20one-of-a-kind%20adventure%20experiences.%20In%20this%20way%20we%20strive%20to%20play%20a%20powerful%20role%20in%20raising%20awareness,%20shaping%20attitudes,%20and%20improving%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20we%20collectively%20interact%20with%20nature.%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar%20wilderness%20is%20experience%20unprecedented%20threat%20from%20explosive%20growth%20in%20adventure%20tourism%20and%20local%20economic%20ambitions.%20Again,%20there%20are%20few%20environmental%20laws%20to%20regulate%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20companies%20practice,%20and%20even%20fewer%20authorities%20to%20enforce%20them.%20The%20result%20is,%20again%20a%20%22self-governed%22%20industry%20that%20depends%20greatly%20on%20its%20leaders%20to%20maintain%20a%20culture%20of%20environmental%20integrity%20by%20setting%20good%20examples.%20Again%20we%20recognize%20and%20honor,%20and%20fell%20more%20and%20more%20an%20increased%20responsibility%20to%20protect%20and%20preserved%20these%20wild%20places%20and%20this%20is%20the%20message%20we%20convey%20to%20everyone.%20It%20is%20of%20the%20utmost%20importance%20to%20all%20of%20us%20that%20our%20interaction%20with%20the%20people%20we%20encounter%20along%20the%20way%20be%20positive%20and%20mutually%20beneficial%20and%20we%20treat%20every%20area%20as%20if%20it%20was%20our%20home.%20We%20provide%20real%20benefits%20to%20local%20economy,%20employing%20and%20training%20staff,%20purchasing%20all%20supplies%20and%20services%20locally,%20and%20supporting%20people%20in%20the%20areas%20we%20visit%20for%20sustainable%20development%20with%20providing%20such%20as%20medical,%20education,%20sports,%20environment%20campaign%20in%20community%20and%20providing%20dustbin.%20Why%20is%20this%20so%20important%20to%20us?%20Because%20adventure%20was%20once%20our%20passion%20before%20it%20was%20our%20business.%20Today,%20it%20still%20is.%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20has%20taken%20significant%20steps%20towards%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Himalayan%20environment%20and%20the%20people%20who%20live%20here.%20If%20you%20would%20like%20to%20know%20how%20you%20can%20help,%20please%20contact%20us%20because%20we%20are%20running%20our%20Himalayan%20Community%20Project%20(HCP)%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20in%20rural%20areas%20as%20well%20as%20badly%20damage%20villages%20by%20April%202015%20Earthquake%20in%20Nepal.%0A%3C/p%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%09%3Cstrong%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20your%20vacation%20especial.%20%3C/strong%3EThrough%20sharing%20our%20love%20and%20passion%20of%20the%20outdoors%20adventures,%20mountains,%20rock,%20rivers%20and%20jungles%20and%20the%20incredible%20both%20countries%20through%20which%20they%20run%20we%20hope%20to%20make%20authentic%20holidays%20adventure%20and%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20places%20that%20you%20will%20want%20to%20return%20to%20again%20and%20again.%0A%3C/p%3E\"}'),
