(3269, 3098, '1508305244273_data', '{\"id\":\"1508305244273\",\"shortcode\":\"ppb_text\",\"ppb_text_title\":\"before%20experience\",\"ppb_text_layout\":\"\",\"ppb_text_background\":\"\",\"ppb_text_background_parallax\":\"\",\"ppb_text_custom_css\":\"padding-bottom:%200px\",\"ppb_text_content\":\"%5Btg_header%20title=%22WELCOME%20TO%20NEPALAYA%20EXPLORER%22%20,%20subtitle=%22YOUR%20ADVENTURE%20GURU%22%5D%0A%0A%3Cb%3EDear%20Guest,%20We%20at%20Nepalaya%20Explorer%20Love%20Adventure!%3C/b%3E%0A%0AAdventure,%20this%20is%20what%20we%20do%20best!%20We%20are%20based%20in%20Kathmandu,%20Nepal.%20With%20us%20adventure%20is%20something%20that%20everyone%20can%20participate;%20we%E2%80%99ll%20love%20sharing%20these%20places%20with%20you%20and%20passion%20with%20our%20nature.%20We%20specialized%20in%20taking%20our%20old%20and%20new%20friends%20(that%E2%80%99s%20you!)%20in%20real%20authentic%20outdoor%20adventures%20tours.%20Our%20adventures%20bring%20you%20those%20places%20where%20very%20few%20people%20venture%20or%20some%20places%20%E2%80%9CNo%20One%20Before%E2%80%9D!%20Firstly,%20these%20areas%20are%20far%20and%20hard%20to%20reach%20out%20there,%20which%20offer%20a%20real%20chance%20to%20relax%20and%20switch%20off%20from%20everyday%20modern%20life%20back%20to%20home.%20%20Places%20you%20venture%20are%20remote,%20wild,%20untouched,%20unspoiled,%20unpolluted,%20unexplored,%20challenging%20and%20most%20scenic,%20most%20exciting%20and%20most%20beautiful%20places%20of%20Nepal%20and%20Myanmar%20Himalayas,%20and%20offering%20a%20unique%20chance%20to%20view%20beauty%20of%20nature,%20wildlife%20and%20meet%20local%20tribes%20closely,%20get%20a%20genuine%20feel%20for%20their%20culture%20and%20observed%20how%20people%20really%20lives%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mountain%20terraces.%20We%20have%20specialized%20in%20Mountaineering,%20Trekking,%20Rafting,%20Rock%20Climbing,%20Caving,%20Canyoning-%20and%20multi%20activity%20and,%20sustainable%20charity%20challenge%20events!%20Our%20adventures%20are%20designed%20and%20run%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20providing%20the%20highest%20quality%20experience.%20There%20is%20just%20the%20rhythms%20of%20nature,%20as%20you%20sleep%20with%20soothing%20sound%20of%20the%20water%20near%20by%20the%20river%20or%20up%20closed%20on%20top%20of%20the%20Himalaya%20under%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstarry%20starry%20milky%20way%E2%80%9D%20campsites%20or%20we%20prefer%20to%20say%20(%E2%80%9Cone%20million%20star%20or%20full%20moon%20nights%E2%80%9D)%20the%20warm%20sun%20to%20kiss%20you%20awake%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20misty%20snow-capped%20mountains%20as%20your%20first%20view%20when%20you%20open%20your%20eyes,%20and%20during%20the%20day%20introduce%20you%20with%20people%20and%20their%20culture%20and,%20nature%20which%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20change%20from%20centuries.%20We%20feast%20you%20with%20Himalayas%20naturally%20grew%20fresh%20organic%20vegetables,%20fruits%20and%20delicious%20food%20prepared%20by%20your%20adventure%20master%20chef,%20accompanied%20by%20apr%C3%A8s-adventure%20drinks,%20and%20entertaining%20professional%20multi%20knowledge%20adventure%20guides!%20With%20our%20strong%20focus%20on%20sustainable%20Eco-and%20community-support%20tourism,%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20offer%20you%20unique%20and%20unmatched%20multi%20adventure%20itineraries,%20which%20can%20be%20found%20only%20with%20us.%20Be%20warned:%20adventure%20with%20us%20may%20even%20change%20your%20life%20and%20country%20Too.\"}'),
