ures are designed and run in the spirit of providing the highest quality experience. There is just the rhythms of nature, as you sleep with soothing sound of the water near by the river or up closed on top of the Himalaya under the “starry starry milky way” campsites or we prefer to say (“one million star or full moon nights”) the warm sun to kiss you awake in the morning and misty snow-capped mountains as your first view when you open your eyes, and during the day introduce you with people and their culture and, nature which hasn’t change from centuries. We feast you with Himalayas naturally grew fresh organic vegetables, fruits and delicious food prepared by your adventure master chef, accompanied by après-adventure drinks, and entertaining professional multi knowledge adventure guides! With our strong focus on sustainable Eco-and community-support tourism, we are proud to offer you unique and unmatched multi adventure itineraries, which can be found only with us. Be warned: adventure with us may even change your life and country Too.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"ppb_tour one withpadding \" ><div class=\"page_content_wrapper full_width\" style=\"text-align:center\"><h2 class=\"ppb_title\">Itineraries that Inspires You</h2><div class=\"page_caption_desc\">As remote as it gets, Antarctica used to be the preserve of only the hardiest of explorers</div><div class=\"portfolio_filter_wrapper three_cols fullwidth shortcode gallery section content clearfix\"><div class=\"element portfolio3filter_wrapper\"><div class=\"one_third gallery3 filterable gallery_type animated1\"><a href=\"http://dac.technocreates.net/nepalayaexplorer/tours/absolute-nepal-adventure/\">\r\n        		    <img src=\"http://dac.technocreates.net/nepalayaexplorer/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/nepalaya_explorer_suspension_bridge_nepal-560x460.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n        		</a><div class=\"thumb_content fullwidth \"><div class=\"thumb_title\"><div class=\"tour_country\">\r\n	            		Nepal\r\n	   